# 🛰 NetPulse AI Monitor

Real-time network monitoring system for Google & YouTube services with AI-powered congestion detection and email notifications.

## ✨ Features

- **Real-time Monitoring**: Live data from ThingSpeak API
- **AI Predictions**: Machine learning model for congestion detection
- **Email Notifications**: Automatic alerts for network issues
- **Historical Analytics**: Track network performance over time
- **Ultra-modern UI**: Cyberpunk holographic theme

